            <h2>Inclement Weather</h2>
            <p>
                On occasion, due to the unpredictable nature of coastal living,
                work may need to be rescheduled due to heavy rain or storm
                activity, high winds, bushfires and the like. Rescheduling will
                place the booking in the next appropriate available time slot.
            </p>

            <h2>Cancellations</h2>
            <p>
                We understand life can take many unexpected turns. Please notify
                us as soon as you can about the need to reschedule or cancel a
                booking. We will happily reschedule your booking if the weather
