                Cheques to be made payable to “Simon Albore”. Cash payments are
                also welcome. Overdue invoices may incur a late fee of 5% of the
                invoice total.
            </p>

            <h2>Non Payments</h2>
            <p>
                Failure to pay overdue invoices in their entirety will result in
                the engagement of debt recovery services. All costs of debt
                recovery will be passed on the debtor in addition to any
                existing debt and interest already incurred.
            </p>

            <h2>Digital Media</h2>
            <p>
                Our place of work varies from location to location.
                Photographing work sites to highlight access and safety issues
                for staff will be necessary from time to time. The photographs
                may also be used in the quoting and estimation process. These
                photos are discarded on completion of the job. On occasion
                workers may be photographed carrying out work related tasks for
                use on social media and business promotion. No location or
                personal information is ever recorded. Please advise our staff
                if you do not wish for photos to be used for social media and
                promotion purposes.
            </p>
